#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.20/guides/security-jwt-build.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "You can sign the claims and then encrypt the nested JWT token by combining the sign and encrypt steps."
msgstr "您可以先对声明进行签名，然后通过将签名和加密步骤结合起来，对嵌套的 JWT 令牌进行加密。"

