msgstr "不过，请注意，不建议在配置中直接内联私钥。仅当需要从远程密钥管理器中获取签名密钥值时，才应使用 `smallrye.jwt.sign.key` 属性。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.20/guides/security-jwt-build.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The keys can also be loaded by the code that builds the token, and then supplied to JWT Build API for token creation."
msgstr "这些密钥也可以由生成令牌的代码加载，然后提供给 JWT Build API 以用于创建令牌。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/3.20/guides/security-jwt-build.adoc
#, fuzzy
